    "legend": null
  },
  {
    "title": "Capacity Used %",
    "promql": [
      "rustfs_cluster_capacity_used_bytes",
      "rustfs_cluster_capacity_usable_total_bytes"
    ],
    "unit": "percent",
    "chartType": "stat",
    "thresholds": [
      { "color": "green", "value": null },
      { "color": "orange", "value": 70 },
      { "color": "red", "value": 90 }
    ],
    "legend": null,
    "note": "比值面板：used/usable_total*100"
  },
  {
    "title": "Drives Online / Offline",
    "promql": [
      "rustfs_cluster_health_drives_online_count",
      "rustfs_cluster_health_drives_offline_count"
    ],
    "unit": "short",
    "chartType": "stat",
    "thresholds": [
      { "color": "green", "value": null },
      { "color": "red", "value": 1 }
    ],
    "legend": null,
    "note": "另存在 rustfs_system_drive_online_count/_offline_count 平行指标族，语义近似未完全消歧，选 cluster_health 前缀作集群总览口径"
  },
  {
    "title": "S3 Operations by API",
    "promql": ["rustfs_s3_operations_total"],
    "unit": "ops",
    "chartType": "timeseries",
    "thresholds": null,
    "legend": "op",
    "note": "counter，rate 后 by(op) 分系列；2026-07-04 实测覆盖 13 种 S3 动词（Put/Get/Head/List/Copy/Delete/Multipart 等）"
  },
  {
